Summary of MSS ('07', '01', '02', '03', '04', '05', '09', '011', '013', '017', '019', '021', '022', '024', '026', '028', '029') for John's Gospel

This page shows the differences, per verse, for selected manuscripts. Each variant (of a verse) is assigned a letter. The first manuscript will always show 'a' for each verse that is present, and the next variant of that verse to be found will be 'b', and so on.
